@jluebbe thanks for reporting! Indeed `writer` was removed by accident while trying to revert 05cfdcc which rendered `_tw` read-only while preparing for 3.3 in #2945. The reason for that revert is because `pytest-instafail` plugin attempts to set `_tw` to something else. ðŸ˜ž 

Not sure how to proceed here to be honest. Removing `writer` was a mistake, but I'm thinking re-adding `TerminalReporter.writer` only to deprecate it in the next release will only add to the confusion further. Opinions?

@RonnyPfannschmidt @The-Compiler
